author: Solid jj
description:
The Justice League face one of the greatest threats to any group of friends; financial instability! Superman, Batman, Aquaman, Green Lantern, Flash, Wonder Woman (and the rest) race against time to see if they can raise enough funds filming some good 'ol fashioned PSAs before the Justice League goes bankrupt. Also Hawkman is here, he requested we say that.
